<h2 id="hd_id3145792">File Name </h2>
      <paragraph id="par_id3150206" role="paragraph"><ahelp hid="modules/scalc/ui/headerfootercontent/buttonBTN_FILE">Inserts a file name placeholder in the selected area.</ahelp> Click to insert the title. Long-click <comment>UFI: this is still a long-click</comment>to select either title, file name or path/file name from the submenu. If a title has not be assigned (see <emph>File - Properties</emph>), the file name will be inserted instead.</paragraph>
